'''Ariana''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Garos IV]]. It boasted the [[University of Garos]], [[The Violet Viska]], and [[Chado's Pub]]. To the south lay the [[Tahika Cliffs]] and a mining base at the foot of [[Mount Usca]], to which it was connected by the [[Currahen Crossroad]]. To the west was the [[Locura Ocean]].

